valida_etapa:: [[PAG-001-INT-PAGTO]]

---

## SQL
```sql
SELECT count(*) AS qtd_erros
FROM (
    SELECT contrato, produto, dt_ref
    FROM view_silver_integrado
    GROUP BY 1,2,3
    HAVING count(*) > 1
)
````

---

## Regra

